### Type of computer application

This particular discourse centers on [trustless](/Trustless_system) [decentralized applications](/Decentralization) (DApps), those digital phantoms that promise autonomy without the usual human oversight. For those whose minds wander to other permutations of distributed digital constructs, one might consider delving into the broader realm of [distributed computing](/Distributed_computing) – though, frankly, the distinctions often feel like splitting hairs on a ghost.

